# Dice Roller

Interactive Python dice rolling simulator that allows users to choose the number of dice and the number of sides per die.

## Features

- User-defined number of dice
- User-defined number of sides
- Random dice roll generation
- Replay option
- Clean command-line output

## Skills Demonstrated

- Python Fundamentals
- User Input Handling
- While Loops
- For Loops
- Random Number Generation
- String Formatting
- Conditional Logic

